data.description: Welcome to 780 Old Mount Dora Rd in Eustis. Great location only a mile from 441 with shopping and restaurants so close by. It has a split bedroom floor plan and and open living floor plan. The kitchen has an abundance of wood 42inch cabinets for storage and ample amount of stone counters to prepare meals. Newer Stainless steel appliances accompany this 17x10 kitchen. The kitchen looks out to a spacious family room with hard wood floors. The large living room  (26x14) combined with dining room also has hard wood floors,  has ton of natural light and is great for entertaining. The master bedroom, family room and living room all come with highly efficient air conditioner splits that create a comfortable environment. The property over a 1/4 of an acre is completely fenced in and has an outdoor wood patio deck to enjoy year round. In the back yard there is a huge work shed. ROOF SOLAR PLANELS ARE INCLUDED FOR UTILITY EFFICENCY. A spacious 2-car garage, indoor laundry room. NO HOA. MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT TODAY.
